Package: eclust
Title: Time Series Clustering using Energy Distance
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("Leon", "Fernandes", , "leon.fernandes@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7192-9939"))
Maintainer: Leon Fernandes <leon.fernandes@columbia.edu>
Description: This package implements the multivariate time series clustering algorithm from Davis et al. 2022 (doi: 10.1111/jtsa.12688). The method is based on a pairwise multivariate distance covaraince metric followed by a hierarchical clustering procedure to obtain the final clusters.
